Define The Business Needs - Questions to Ask

What is really needed? 
This is in terms of your value proposition.
What will happen if nothing is done about it?
Answer this by standing in the shoes of your client.
How are their needs changing?
Answer this by understanding where your client is on their journey.
What do you see happening in the next 3 years?
Think of this in terms of industry developments and trends.
Who are you competitors and collaborators?
How do your plans fit into what others are doing
